                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "You are an artist, and you have been preparing to hone your craft according to the traditions of Prismari College. Whatever your medium-sculpture, dance, paint, music, drama, architecture, or any other field-you have grand visions of bringing your art to life in a fusion of magic and creativity."
